  "title": "v1.128.0",
  "summary": "What's Changed Remove unused video extension extraction in Share extension by @mozzius in #11081 Update lint-staged by @mozzius in #11084 Fix KWS language picker silently resetting Arabic, Chinese, Filipino & Portuguese to English by @surfdude29 in #11082 Update KWS supported languages and mapping by @surfdude29 in #11085 Replace @tiptap/html generateJSON w…",
  "content": "<h2>What&#x27;s Changed</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Remove unused video extension extraction in Share extension by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11081\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11081</a></li>\n<li>Update lint-staged by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11084\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11084</a></li>\n<li>Fix KWS language picker silently resetting Arabic, Chinese, Filipino &amp; Portuguese to English by <a href=\"https://github.com/surfdude29\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@surfdude29</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11082\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11082</a></li>\n<li>Update KWS supported languages and mapping by <a href=\"https://github.com/surfdude29\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@surfdude29</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11085\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11085</a></li>\n<li>Replace @tiptap/html generateJSON with native DOMParser equivalent by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11098\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11098</a></li>\n<li>Slim down CLAUDE.md by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11102\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11102</a></li>\n<li>Migrate all search to v2 and remove v1 by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11125\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11125</a></li>\n<li>restore v1.128.0 by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11131\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11131</a></li>\n<li>Fix crash when maxHeight is nil at sheet presentation by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11104\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11104</a></li>\n<li>Potentially fix disappearing chat emoji on some devices by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11113\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11113</a></li>\n<li>Lazy load @ipld/dag-cbor in computeCid by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11099\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11099</a></li>\n<li>pnpm 11.11.0 by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11130\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11130</a></li>\n<li>Migrate to Oxlint by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10384\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10384</a></li>\n<li>Collapse label appeal flow into ModerationDetailsDialog by <a href=\"https://github.com/amckinley\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@amckinley</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11091\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11091</a></li>\n<li>Ensure long trending topic titles can wrap by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11141\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11141</a></li>\n<li>Prototype: Show known likers on post thread page by <a href=\"https://github.com/abenzer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@abenzer</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11080\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11080</a></li>\n<li>Bump the actions group with 6 updates by <a href=\"https://github.com/dependabot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@dependabot</a>[bot] in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11148\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11148</a></li>\n<li>Update Sentry to 8.x by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11147\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11147</a></li>\n<li>Typescript 7 by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11109\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11109</a></li>\n<li>Create primary tooltip variant by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11140\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11140</a></li>\n<li>Allow up to 10 images in share intent by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11132\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11132</a></li>\n<li>Add video playback observability to Sentry by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11111\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11111</a></li>\n<li>Revert &quot;Typescript 7&quot; by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11152\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11152</a></li>\n<li>Stub out react-native-svg fetchData on web to drop buffer polyfill by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11097\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11097</a></li>\n<li>fix web feed footer clearing the bottom bar by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11151\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11151</a></li>\n<li>[APP-2642] Social proof text is truncated on mobile by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11155\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11155</a></li>\n<li>fix android carousel jiggle from cdn-rounded aspect ratio by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11153\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11153</a></li>\n<li>Add setting for opting in to beta features by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11123\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11123</a></li>\n<li>Strip leading @ in from: queries by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11158\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11158</a></li>\n<li>Upgrade pnpm to 11.13.0 by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11163\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11163</a></li>\n<li>Remove IS_INTERNAL check for beta feedback button by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11162\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11162</a></li>\n<li>Don&#x27;t suggest retrying an unretryable error by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11159\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11159</a></li>\n<li>Log additional context for post:* events by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11035\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11035</a></li>\n<li>Add DM button to labeller profiles by <a href=\"https://github.com/RetroSunstar\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@RetroSunstar</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11149\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11149</a></li>\n<li>Fix invisible bidi characters copied with handles on web by <a href=\"https://github.com/a-y-ibrahim\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@a-y-ibrahim</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11066\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11066</a></li>\n<li>Add mark requests as read to chat settings menu by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11107\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11107</a></li>\n<li>Update SVGO by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11083\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11083</a></li>\n<li>Add Japan-gated custom logo by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11161\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11161</a></li>\n<li>v1.128.0 release prep by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11167\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11167</a></li>\n<li>use pnpm 11.13.1 by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11168\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11168</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>New Contributors</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/a-y-ibrahim\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@a-y-ibrahim</a> made their first contribution in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11066\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11066</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Full Changelog</strong>: <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/compare/1.127.1...1.128.0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">1.127.1...1.128.0</a></p>",
